{
  "texts": [
    "C. Dataset Building and AugmentationOur first stage focuses on creating a dataset for fine-tuning an LLM.",
    "The existing dataset from [1] has two limitations.",
    "First, it is primarily for jailbreaking ChatGPT, and may not be effecive over other services.",
    "Therefore, it is necessary to universalize it across different LLM chatbots.",
    "This dataset contains prompts with specific terms like \"ChatGPT\" or \"Ope-nAI\"."
  ]
}